# Privacy Policy for Gulahati Vendor App


This Privacy Policy describes how Gulahati Vendor App collects, uses, and shares information about you when you use our mobile application ("App") as a vendor or home-based business owner. By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

## Information We Collect

### 1. Information You Provide
- Product details and images
- Customer information (name, contact details, delivery address)
- Order details (products, quantities, payment information if applicable)

### 2. Automatically Collected Information
- Usage data (features accessed, time and duration of activities, error logs)

## How We Use Your Information

1. To Provide and Improve Our Services
2. Communication with users
3. Analytics for service improvement

## Information Sharing

We do not sell, trade, or transfer personal information for marketing purposes. However, we may share your information:
- With service providers
- In response to legal requests or to comply with laws

## Data Retention

We retain information for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy unless a longer retention period is required by law.

## Your Rights

You may have rights regarding your personal information, including access, correction, or deletion. Contact us at info@access-itech.com to exercise these rights.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Material changes will be notified through the App or by email.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our practices regarding your personal information, please contact us at info@access-itech.com.

By using the Gulahati Vendor App, you consent to the collection and use of your information as described in this Privacy Policy.
